comments: Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) brings his hand toward Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs during Bogdanovic's drive.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) extends his hand to contest Bogdanovic's (ATL) driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs after the release.
Bazley (OKC) jumps to contest Capela's (ATL) dunk attempt, and marginal body contact occurs as Capela starts his upward shooting motion.
Collins (ATL) brings both hands forward to Williams' (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs during his drive.
Collins' (ATL) initiates body contact as he jumps to contest Bazley's (OKC) shot attempt near the rim.
Bazley (OKC) brings his arm toward Young's (ATL) front and marginal contact occurs during Young's drive.
Young (ATL) is moving toward Giddey's (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs at the end of Giddey's drive.
Collins (ATL) maintains verticality and absorbs the oncoming contact that occurs during Giddey's (OKC) driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) slightly extends his arm forward to Murray's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs during Murray's drive.
Murray (ATL) lifts his arm slightly and marginal contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander during the drive.
Murray (ATL) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball. Possession is correctly awarded to OKC.
Young (ATL) is moving alongside Giddey's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs when they come together during the drive.
Young (ATL) brings his arm slightly forward and marginal contact occurs with Giddey's (OKC) back, as he releases away during the driving shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) is already in Williams (OKC) path as marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Williams (OKC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Young (ATL) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Williams (OKC) commits a take foul on Collins (ATL).
Murray (ATL) is moving alongside of Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and makes contact with the ball during his driving shot attempt.
Collins' (ATL) arm is moving into a vertical position when it brushes Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) head during his layup attempt. The contact that occurs is incidental.
Giddey (OKC) commits a take foul on Murray (ATL).
